reviewText: This 2 disk DVD jam cam chronicles is stuffed with amazing jams from the Disco Biscuits, Umphrey's Mcgee, Perpetual groove among other jam band super starts. The Disco Biscuits play on of my personal favorites "the very moon." Not only does it have this it also has interviews with Marc Brownstein talking about head count. Another amazing hit light is the all star jam of turn on your head light by The New Sounds of San Francisco w/ members of Tea Leaf Green, ALO, Hot Buttered Rum. This is a must have to anyone trying to see what Wakarusa was just a fee years ago.
